    pageEncoding="UTF-8"%>
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
</head>
<body>
	<div class="how_to_use_div">
		<h2>요청사항이 진행되는 과정</h2>
		<div class="how_container">
			<div class="how_to">

				<img width="50" src="${contextPath}/resources/images/stat/001-new.png" >

				
				<h3>신규 작성</h3>
				<p>요청사항 게시판에<br> <b>신규</b>로 글을 작성합니다.</p>
				
			</div>
			
			
			
			
			<div class="how_to">
				<img width="50" src="${contextPath}/resources/images/stat/002-checkmark.png">
				<h3>담당자 접수</h3>
				<p>관리자가 글을 확인 후<br><b>접수</b>합니다.</p>

			</div>

			
			<div class="how_to">
				<img width="50" src="${contextPath}/resources/images/stat/003-loading.png">
				<h3>진행</h3>
				<p>관리자가 문제를 <br><b>해결 중</b>입니다.</p>
			</div>

			
			<div class="how_to">
				<img width="50" src="${contextPath}/resources/images/stat/004-complete.png">
				<h3>완료</h3>
				<p>관리자가 요청사항을 <br><b>해결 완료</b>했습니다.</p>

			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

</body>
</html>